>plz"},{"pid":"1438cd04a389561458d1c80f168b9c73356ca5a8","tid":1615084,"uid":176484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T03:58:10.000Z","msg":"幫幫消防<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />plz"},{"pid":"ee8deb2dc99616d3eeac64c733065b7147497081","tid":1615084,"uid":176484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T03:58:47.000Z","msg":"幫幫消防<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />plz"},{"pid":"4bcd7b317ab069e6a467c467eb6f3699eaa7ecb4","tid":1615084,"uid":125582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T03:59:20.000Z","msg":"但係最大果個唔係撐警咩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8020580722ca4381ac32c1a3df96baf7f90b4de","tid":1615084,"uid":158815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T03:59:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06d5ec24464e6a628bd0d5e6ff81697365216e05","tid":1615084,"uid":35090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T04:04:09.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4c7507b1466630d126708c6e97754737a41e53ef","tid":1615084,"uid":226740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T04:07:15.000Z","msg":"push &amp; sent"},{"pid":"88726e6ee8f2c52f678a6104ae99e2a8d62f2e5f","tid":1615084,"uid":56751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T04:08:12.000Z","msg":"希望巴打唔介意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我改一改左英文版再精䉮啲 share下<br />\n<br />\nTo the Director of Fire Services Mr. Li Kin-yat,<br />\n<br />\nRecently, two firemen were aggressively criticised since 29 September for they have rescued local citizens who were stuck in an MTR station. In the midst of beliefs confrontation with various political stands, the act of saving lives should by no means be compromised. It is the firemen&rsquo;s responsibility to rescue anyone in danger regardless of the victim&rsquo;s criminal records, political stands, or any external circumstances. And this was the principle the two firemen had obeyed. <br />\n<br />\nIt is our sincere hope that Hong Kong Fire Services Department will not succumb to political pressure and uphold the department&rsquo;s mission in order to protect lives of Hong Kong citizens. A wise decision be made earns the trust in general public. We appreciate if the 2 firefighters who completed their job mission can be protected and defended. <br />\n<br />\nThank you for your attention in this matter.<br />\n<br />\nHong Kong citizens,<br />\nOctober XX, 2019<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">救同路人，一齊send</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"15ca7d1b2602f320fd06998436a8c19374b7f406","tid":1615084,"uid":215947,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T04:08:43.000Z","msg":"done"},{"pid":"6efc6d4a0ceaacee84e47e0bf495975645271ae2","tid":1615084,"uid":56751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"15ca7d1b2602f320fd06998436a8c19374b7f406","tid":1615084,"uid":215947,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T04:08:43.000Z","msg":"done"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T04:11:23.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ac5df44ae9258803ef3bf19d2059c7b133be0139","tid":1615084,"uid":232671,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T04:12:08.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"273d08f600c5a71b7de4068d9f681b5047594efb","tid":1615084,"uid":176484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"88726e6ee8f2c52f678a6104ae99e2a8d62f2e5f","tid":1615084,"uid":56751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T04:08:12.000Z","msg":"希望巴打唔介意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我改一改左英文版再精䉮啲 share下<br />\n<br />\nTo the Director of Fire Services Mr. Li Kin-yat,<br />\n<br />\nRecently, two firemen were aggressively criticised since 29 September for they have rescued local citizens who were stuck in an MTR station. In the midst of beliefs confrontation with various political stands, the act of saving lives should by no means be compromised. It is the firemen&rsquo;s responsibility to rescue anyone in danger regardless of the victim&rsquo;s criminal records, political stands, or any external circumstances. And this was the principle the two firemen had obeyed. <br />\n<br />\nIt is our sincere hope that Hong Kong Fire Services Department will not succumb to political pressure and uphold the department&rsquo;s mission in order to protect lives of Hong Kong citizens. A wise decision be made earns the trust in general public. We appreciate if the 2 firefighters who completed their job mission can be protected and defended. <br />\n<br />\nThank you for your attention in this matter.<br />\n<br />\nHong Kong citizens,<br />\nOctober XX, 2019<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">救同路人，一齊send</span></span></strong>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T04:13:34.000Z","msg":"好<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4de6a24a3934cb1bfda1950fa9295514e640fa7a","tid":1615084,"uid":56751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"273d08f600c5a71b7de4068d9f681b5047594efb","tid":1615084,"uid":176484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"88726e6ee8f2c52f678a6104ae99e2a8d62f2e5f","tid":1615084,"uid":56751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T04:08:12.000Z","msg":"希望巴打唔介意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我改一改左英文版再精䉮啲 share下<br />\n<br />\nTo the Director of Fire Services Mr. Li Kin-yat,<br />\n<br />\nRecently, two firemen were aggressively criticised since 29 September for they have rescued local citizens who were stuck in an MTR station. In the midst of beliefs confrontation with various political stands, the act of saving lives should by no means be compromised. It is the firemen&rsquo;s responsibility to rescue anyone in danger regardless of the victim&rsquo;s criminal records, political stands, or any external circumstances. And this was the principle the two firemen had obeyed. <br />\n<br />\nIt is our sincere hope that Hong Kong Fire Services Department will not succumb to political pressure and uphold the department&rsquo;s mission in order to protect lives of Hong Kong citizens. A wise decision be made earns the trust in general public. We appreciate if the 2 firefighters who completed their job mission can be protected and defended. <br />\n<br />\nThank you for your attention in this matter.<br />\n<br />\nHong Kong citizens,<br />\nOctober XX, 2019<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">救同路人，一齊send</span></span></strong>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T04:13:34.000Z","msg":"好<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T04:14:03.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"754f76989fff55759b56fcc728745d5560c021df","tid":1615084,"uid":205269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T04:14:30.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"cb58e2776ea9bcced5d72773b96a9562ddbd0cf4","tid":1615084,"uid":176484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bfe498bc7e03c7536c32cf0e91adcb8ff7e48d65","tid":1615084,"uid":176484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T03:36:07.000Z","msg":"廣傳！請大家寫信表揚英勇救人、盡忠職守的消防員！有人問左消防員朋友，證實寫信是真的有用的！<br />\n<br />\n星期日，喺金鐘站英勇救人的兩位消防員宜家俾藍絲攻擊，要求炒佢。特別係其中一位消防員佢剛剛入職，未過probation！請大家用自己Email寫去消防處總部/灣仔消防局，讚揚呢個消防員盡忠職守，不分政見，拯救市民。<br />\n<br />\nsend去消防處總部：<br />\nhkfsdenq@hkfsd.gov.hk<br />\n或者灣仔消防局：<br />\nwch_fstn@hkfsd.gov.hk<br />\n<br />\n敬啟者：本人認為救傷扶危是消防人員的天職，也是最無可爭議的偉大工作。可是近日（9月29日）二名消防人員因為解救被困在金鐘地鐵站內的市民而飽受抨擊（被質疑幫助違法市民），欲加之罪，本人深感震驚！按理消防人員無法辨認被困市民曾否犯法，這並非消防職務，消防人員遇上市民被困，本分是應協助市民解困，至於拘捕疑犯，搜證調查乃係警務人員之工作。本人希望除向兩位消防人表達謝意！同時希望消防局不要因為政治壓力，扭曲消防員的守責行為。如此方不負社會對消防之期望！<br />\n<br />\n此致<br />\n消防處長<br />\n<br />\n市民XXX<br />\n2-10-19<br />\n<br />\n俾多個英文版，通常回覆英文信都會認真同埋快好多，繼續去信，中英文都要<br />\n<br />\nTo the Director of Fire Services Mr. Li Kin-yat,<br />\n<br />\nWith utmost respect, firefighters are some of the most selfless public servants our society has ever encountered. These real heroes are men who fall and fail and are flawed, but win out in the end because they&rsquo;ve stayed true to their ideals and beliefs and commitments.<br />\n<br />\nUnfortunately, two firemen were aggressively criticised after they rescued local citizens who were stuck in an MTR station on September 29, 2019. When it comes to saving lives, political views or personal beliefs should not interfere with the sacred act of rescuing. It&rsquo;s not a fireman&rsquo;s duty to determine whether or not the victim has or has not committed any crime prior to the rescue effort, a fireman should be there to help any victim regardless of his/her background.<br />\n<br />\nIt is my sincere hope that Hong Kong Fire Services Department will not succumb to political pressure and uphold the department&rsquo;s mission to protect life of Hong Kong citizens, to save those in distress and protect the community. Rest assured that you and your department will continue to be recognised and supported by the majority of the general public if you can defend these 2 selfless firefighters and uphold the department's mission.<br />\n<br />\nThank you for your kind attention into the matter.<br />\n<br />\nA concerned Hong Kong citizen,<br />\nXXX<br />\nOctober XX, 2019"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T04:14:56.000Z","msg":"更新英文版<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nTo the Director of Fire Services Mr. Li Kin-yat,<br />\n<br />\nRecently, two firemen were aggressively criticised since 29 September for they have rescued local citizens who were stuck in an MTR station. In the midst of beliefs confrontation with various political stands, the act of saving lives should by no means be compromised. It is the firemen&rsquo;s responsibility to rescue anyone in danger regardless of the victim&rsquo;s criminal records, political stands, or any external circumstances. And this was the principle the two firemen had obeyed. <br />\n<br />\nIt is our sincere hope that Hong Kong Fire Services Department will not succumb to political pressure and uphold the department&rsquo;s mission in order to protect lives of Hong Kong citizens. A wise decision be made earns the trust in general public. We appreciate if the 2 firefighters who completed their job mission can be protected and defended. <br />\n<br />\nThank you for your attention in this matter.<br />\n<br />\nHong Kong citizens,<br />\nOctober XX, 2019"},{"pid":"8d6e089e6492f398cd9331ad6987842808f92a21","tid":1615084,"uid":157275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T04:15:07.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b5639233a0d025c6f167d006416d8d4ef9aabc39","tid":1615084,"uid":130705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T04:15:17.000Z","msg":"sent and push<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33701e0391c7f89fd135bebb49b8a7381724d1eb","tid":1615084,"uid":216992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T04:15:33.000Z","msg":"高端化妝之學術討論<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1615130\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1615130</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"b0ccc86ac745dfc4626d9cac5eaf62b6827c7286","tid":1615084,"uid":112742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T04:15:40.000Z","msg":"Push"}]}